    "f_chart_rationale": "Operator UX: Director hosts multi-position artifacts (thingalog has 6 positions + 2 jobs; openbraid-org has 3 positions). Flat 'Available positions' list answers 'what can I claim right now?' Chart answers 'what is the shape of this org and where do positions fit?' Different mental queries; chart is the more important answer for someone reasoning about org structure. Cross-vendor demo last week made openbraid plausibly protocol-not-vendor; the chart view makes the operator value concrete.",
